OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment pledges         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcrackdown on mobiles in    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschools                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Head teachers in England will be told  
OL,6, to ban pupils from using mobile phones 
OL,7, during the entire school day under new 
OL,8, government guidance.                   
OL,10,FThe Department for Education wants     
OL,11,Fchildren to be barred from using       
OL,12,Fdevices on breaks as well as in class. 
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan will
OL,15,Fannounce the plans at the Conservative 
OL,16,FParty conference on Monday.            
OL,18,FThe government already encourages head 
OL,19,Fteachers to limit phone usage and many 
OL,20,Fschools have restrictions in place.    
